title: Gen Z Vs Millennial: We Were Shocked By These Contenders!
description:
Every day, the generational divide gets bigger and bigger, and it’s especially glaring when you look at technology and pop culture.
So, we’re putting generations to the test with Gen Z vs. Millennial trivia! We have a list of questions for BOTH generations, so let’s see who takes home the money…
